law.catch_line: Application of the provisions of this chapter.
law.text: The provisions of this chapter shall apply to all certificates of birth, death, marriage, divorce, fetal death and induced termination of pregnancy previously received by the Vital Statistics Branch and in the custody of the state registrar or any local registrar.
law.history: Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 443, effective June 20, 2005. -- Created 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 369, sec. 30, effective July 13, 1990.
